<section id="research">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="section-label">Research</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">What I Work On</h2>

    <div class="research-areas">
      <div class="area-card">
        <div class="area-icon">🧠</div>
        <div class="area-title">Neuroergonomics</div>
        <div class="area-desc">Understanding neural and cognitive mechanisms underlying human performance in real-world work environments.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="area-card">
        <div class="area-icon">🤖</div>
        <div class="area-title">Human–Machine Interaction</div>
        <div class="area-desc">Designing assistive devices and exoskeleton systems with integrated mechatronic design and control.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="area-card">
        <div class="area-icon">🛸</div>
        <div class="area-title">Space Human Factors</div>
        <div class="area-desc">Astronaut sensorimotor performance under altered gravity and fatigue — bridging aerospace and human factors.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="area-card">
        <div class="area-icon">📡</div>
        <div class="area-title">Wearable Sensing</div>
        <div class="area-desc">EMG, EEG, and IMU-based systems for real-time physiological monitoring and classification.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="area-card">
        <div class="area-icon">🧬</div>
        <div class="area-title">Biomechanics</div>
        <div class="area-desc">Musculoskeletal analysis and motion capture for understanding human movement and injury risk.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="area-card">
        <div class="area-icon">🔬</div>
        <div class="area-title">Deep Learning</div>
        <div class="area-desc">Temporal models and signal processing for classifying physiological states from multi-modal biosignals.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="current-project">
      <div class="project-label">Current Focus</div>
      <div class="project-title">Astronaut Sensorimotor Performance Under Altered Gravity &amp; Fatigue</div>
      <div class="project-desc">Working with NASA-relevant scenarios to model how fatigue and microgravity compound to degrade human sensorimotor control, with the goal of informing adaptive assistance systems for long-duration spaceflight.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
